* &quot;The Crisis of European Sciences and Transcendental Phenomenology&quot;, 1970 [1936/54], Carr, D., trans. Evanston: Northwestern University Press.
* &quot;Universal Teleology&quot;. &quot;Telos&quot; 4 (Fall 1969). New York: Telos Press.

